item.title: Dart Racer
item.description: Check out early access trailer! Dart Racer is currently my main side project. It’s a VR racing game. Alpha version is out on App Lab or via Side Quest! Early access version with a ton extra content and many upgrades will be out winter 2023 with some luck! Wishlish on App Lab or Steam! Join our Discord community for latest info!
